videos.headline: Hurts uses trickery on big pass play
videos.description: Jalen Hurts quickly tosses back to CeeDee Lamb, who comes across and laterals back to Hurts. Jalen then connects with Nick Basquine on a 70-yard passing play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts uses trickery on big pass play) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurts gets pushed across the goal line for TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts keeps the ball himself and runs into a pile of defenders, but his offensive line pushes the whole pile across the goal line for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts gets pushed across the goal line for TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wildcats' Thompson walks into the end zone for TD
videos.description: Kansas State QB Skylar Thompson calls his own number and waltzes into the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wildcats' Thompson walks into the end zone for TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurts keeps it himself for another TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts takes the snap and finds his way into the end zone for his second rushing touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts keeps it himself for another TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sooners' Motley ejected for kicking Kansas State player
videos.description: After Kansas State RB Joshua Youngblood scores a touchdown, Oklahoma CB Parnell Motley is ejected for kicking Wildcats TE Logan Long.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sooners' Motley ejected for kicking Kansas State player) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sooners' trick play goes horribly wrong
videos.description: Jalen Hurts tosses back to Nick Basquine, who then tries to throw it to Charleston Rambo, but it bounces off his hands and into Kansas State's AJ Parker's for the interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sooners' trick play goes horribly wrong) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson gives Kansas State the lead late in first half
videos.description: Kansas State QB Skylar Thompson keeps the ball himself and rushes 14 yards for a touchdown, his second running score of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Thompson gives Kansas State the lead late in first half) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson extends Wildcats' lead with his third rushing TD
videos.description: Kansas State QB Skylar Thompson maneuvers his way into the end zone for a touchdown to extend the Wildcats' lead over Oklahoma.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Thompson extends Wildcats' lead with his third rushing TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sooners' Pledger fumbles on kickoff return
videos.description: Oklahoma RB. T.J. Pledger fields the kickoff and fumbles the ball as he goes to run, and Kansas State TE Samuel Wheeler recovers it.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sooners' Pledger fumbles on kickoff return) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson helps Wildcats pour it on with fourth rushing score
videos.description: Kansas State QB Skylar Thompson rushes three yards into the end zone for a touchdown to widen the Wildcats' lead over Oklahoma.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Thompson helps Wildcats pour it on with fourth rushing score) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gilbert helps add to Kansas State's lead with TD
videos.description: Kansas State RB James Gilbert walks into the end zone for an easy touchdown to increase the Wildcats' lead over the Oklahoma Sooners.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gilbert helps add to Kansas State's lead with TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lamb evades multiple defenders for 70-yard TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts tosses a short pass to CeeDee Lamb, who escapes multiple defenders on his way to complete a 70-yard touchdown play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lamb evades multiple defenders for 70-yard TD) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurts brings Sooners closer with TD run, 2-point conversion
videos.description: Jalen Hurts scores on a QB sneak and then converts the 2-point conversion on a pass to CeeDee Lamb to bring Oklahoma within 10 of Kansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts brings Sooners closer with TD run, 2-point conversion) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oklahoma's onside kick recovery reversed
videos.description: Oklahoma appears to recover its onside kick attempt, but it gets reversed after officials determined that the ball hit a Sooners player before it traveled 10 yards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oklahoma's onside kick recovery reversed) 2019/10/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson leads Kansas State to upset of Oklahoma
videos.description: Despite a late Sooners rally, Kansas State QB Skylar Thompson rushes for four touchdowns to help the Wildcats defeat No. 5 Oklahoma 48-41.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Thompson leads Kansas State to upset of Oklahoma) 2019/10/26 ESHEET SOTFULL
